comments: Jokic (DEN) and Horton-Tucker (UTA) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Beasley (UTA) cleanly dislodges the ball from Jokic (DEN).  Any ensuing arm contact after the dislodge is considered incidental.
Alexander-Walker (UTA) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Brown (DEN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Olynyk (UTA).
Olynyk (UTA) is bracing for the contact from Jokic (DEN) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Jokic (DEN) and Olynyk (UTA) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Vanderbilt (UTA) is already in Brown's (DEN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Jokic (DEN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Horton-Tucker (UTA) with his left hand before making marginal arm contact with his right.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) and Jokic (DEN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Horton Tucker (UTA) moves slightly forward towards Jokic (DEN) and he absorbs the marginal contact as he contests the shot near the rim.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Alexander-Walker's (UTA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Alexander-Walker (UTA) and Jokic (DEN) briefly engage and disengage after the pick.
Jokic (DEN) is already in Alexander-Walker's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Alexander-Walker (UTA) does not maintain verticality and he makes contact with Jokic's (DEN) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Vanderbilt (UTA) is already in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Vanderbilt (UTA) brings his hands toward Caldwell-Pope (DEN) and marginal contact occurs as Vanderbilt (UTA) releases away to roll.
Brown (DEN) legally contests Alexander-Walker's (UTA) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Vanderbilt (UTA) is out of bounds when he makes contact with the ball.
Horton-Tucker (UTA) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
